### ============================================================
### 系统状态管理接口
### ============================================================

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken =

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 系统状态
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 系统概览 (含 Token 统计、凭据状态、会话数、最近请求等)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 控制面板 (支持 range 参数: 24h / 7d / 30d)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 默认 24 小时
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 近 7 天
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard?range=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 近 30 天
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard?range=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
